就可以退場。<br />\n<br />\n成件事好熟口面，睇嚟歷史又要重演<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e20770ceb56323a565fd254b21d887bd203c977","tid":2197679,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T20:55:04.000Z","msg":"仲有，傾掂左數係唔出奇。因為事實上巴士工會嘅工業行動絕對係有power，只要有返咁上下規模，對政府黎講壓力係唔細。<br />\n<br />\n所以政府搵中間人出嚟同工會暗啞底講數係唔出奇。 所以如果個個都100%下下睇呢啲工會做頭，巴士司機嘅權益就會不知不覺咁樣被出賣。<br />\n<br />\n成件事好可能係2014年嘅翻版，嗰陣味係一模一樣。分別在於當日嘅係泛民做大台，今日就係巴士工會既幹事。 <br />\n<br />\n但如果，呢班所謂嘅巴士工會喺巴士業界中影響力根本微不足道，咁就冇需要擔心了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e756321b8d6d0b89434b64152ab5d95beaf5edd7","tid":2197679,"uid":109459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T21:08:49.000Z","msg":"的士公會？"},{"pid":"1fe1675e0699cdc02a5677c7ce9c23a5b6b22067","tid":2197679,"uid":342786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T21:20:42.000Z","msg":"解散軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25179c53b8cff5a8b228cd8187e1480010811c29","tid":2197679,"uid":276684,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T21:50:34.000Z","msg":"工業行動縮得咁快，咁其它幾間巴士公司仲撐唔撐佢？"},{"pid":"96c13343fbaa8511d67aa2d568961a2edb849abc","tid":2197679,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T23:06:27.000Z","msg":"工賊會？"},{"pid":"833960ed8428153ce598c675efd2b751d28dbba8","tid":2197679,"uid":357803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25179c53b8cff5a8b228cd8187e1480010811c29","tid":2197679,"uid":276684,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T21:50:34.000Z","msg":"工業行動縮得咁快，咁其它幾間巴士公司仲撐唔撐佢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T00:42:55.000Z","msg":"我再諗似乎係一個局<br />\n<br />\n紅簿仔工會梗係講人話引人入局 再搞分化 整到司機士氣潰不成軍"},{"pid":"0391a960bae432687c960b5f46a8dda1fdd3f647","tid":2197679,"uid":40287,"like":0,